metadata.name: Emirates Pass #1
metadata.description: Emirates Pass is a premium discount program that offers unparalleled value and benefits to its members. By joining Emirates Pass, you can enjoy a fantastic 10% discount on all Emirates services, from flights to hotels and more. What's more, Emirates NFT members receive exclusive access to exciting special offers and promotions, ensuring that you always get the best deals possible. With Emirates NFT, you can experience the ultimate in savings and convenience, making every journey more enjoyable than ever before.
